net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.repository.base

Class AbstractSchemaService

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.repository.base.AbstractSchemaService
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultSchemaService

    @Component
 @EnableTransactionManagement(mode=ASPECTJ,
                             proxyTargetClass=true)
public abstract class AbstractSchemaService
extends Object
    Provides schema creation services.

    This class is intended to be used via extension, to allow subclasses to wire in application-specific repositories and provide for their lifecycle, and to allow choice in database binding.
